                <li>Gain hands-on experience with a real-world PDK</li>
                <li>Design and simulate analog, digital, and mixed-signal circuits using only open tools</li>
                <li>Develop practical skills that align with industry and research requirements</li>
                <li>Contribute to the growing global movement for open-source silicon</li>
              </ul>
            
              <p class="text-gray-800">
